<section>
	<h2>Indirect truth tables</h2>
	<p>Contradiction and consistency</p>
	
	<ul>
		<li class="fragment">If a WFF is contradictory, then it can't possibly be true.</li>
		<li class="fragment">So, to test this, we attempt to make it true.</li>
		<li class="fragment">If we can do this then it is actually consistent.</li>
		<li class="fragment">If we run into a contradiction, then Bob's your uncle.</li>
	</ul>

	
	</section>
	
